s/?book=6&chapter=10'>Jos 10</a><br/> b at Hazor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11'>Jos 11</a><br/> - Age of, at death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=8'>Jdg 2:8</a> <br/> 2. An Israelite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=6&verse=14'>1Sa 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=6&verse=18'>1Sa 6:18</a><br/> 3. A governor of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=8'>2Ki 23:8</a><br/> 4. Called Jeshua<br/> - The high priest of the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=2'>Ezr 2:2</a> <br/> - Assist Zerubbabel in restoring the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=13'>Ezr 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=4&verse=6'>Ezr 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=5'>Ezr 5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=1&verse=1'>Hag 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=1&verse=14'>Hag 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=2&verse=2'>Hag 2:2</a> <br/> - Symbolic of the restoration of the church<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=3&verse=10'>Zec 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=15'>Zec 6:15</a> "}]}